text: The 2020 United States presidential straw poll in Guam was held on November 3, 2020. Although Guam is a territory and not a state, ineligible to elect members of the Electoral College. ducts a presidential straw poll to gauge islanders' preference for president every election year. == References == Category:2020 United States presidential election
title: 2020 United States presidential straw poll in Guam
